{"tid":50501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港特色餐廳","createTime":"2016-12-22T12:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T12:44:52.000Z","uid":11735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02ca1ae56bc2a5688f0fe28ea2daa184c5b419be","tid":50501,"uid":11735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:38:49.000Z","msg":"由細到大住左香港咁耐但都up唔出香港有咩特色餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時有啲外國朋友叫我介紹下都唔知答乜好<br />\n又冇理由叫佢地去酒樓去澳牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟香港係咪冇特色？<br />\n巴絲們有咩好推介可以比小弟下次可以推比朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申真係試過帶人地澳牛比人笑到面黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aebb9a8f5446d880dc4f4a96291c2fb4d9e61359","tid":50501,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"掃街？"},{"pid":"ccc0f73cc1a0852f6caf0520fa59693942d88dc1","tid":50501,"uid":11735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>掃街？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n掃街有諗過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔係帶住佢地好難掃到"},{"pid":"1794ea4755ef5f32f0b5f7a224e9729a3b000890","tid":50501,"uid":50100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:44:52.000Z","msg":"好食啲或者傳統啲嘅茶記"}]}